      "layout": "The page uses a maximum content width for key sections but allows for full-bleed elements, such as headers or specific section backgrounds. The hero section often features a split layout with imagery on one side and a brand statement on a colored background (Sand Dune) on the other. Product listings are presented in responsive grid formations, often 2-5 columns, with consistent vertical spacing between items. Navigation is a fixed top bar on larger screens, compacting on smaller views. Sections are primarily divided by changes in background color (Paper White, Sand Dune) or implied by distinct content blocks. Overall density is compact, with element and section gaps creating a rhythmic flow rather than vast whitespace.",
